title: Move In Ready Ranch
posting_body: 3 bedroom, 2 bath, updated ranch, very well kept and neat and clean, living room with newly finished hardwood floors, great light and nicely sized throughout, open kitchen with stainless steel refrigerator, stove and dishwasher

, all bedrooms have hardwood and good closet space, full bath on main level, full basement partially finished , washer and dryer, rec room and ample storage, central air, fenced yard, 2 car detached garage, nice size yard.
No smoking in home and no pets.
